{"name":"Through Death’s Eyes","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you<strong> go into battle</strong>, roll+WIS. • On a 10+, name someone who will live and someone who will die. • On a 7-9, name someone who will live or someone who will die. Name NPCs, not player characters. The GM will make your vision come true, if it’s even remotely possible. • On a 6- you see your own death and consequently take -1 ongoing throughout the battle.</p>","rollType":"WIS","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"czC0Lk9K4LQyVbHB"}
